name: Jamie Josh Mckinney
description: My interests include watching movies while snuggling on the couch, shopping, working out, playing volleyball, hanging out with friends, dancing with a special someone, going out to new restaurants and i love to take part in my partner’s interests, so I would say I am pretty much up for anything.I also enjoy seeing new places, meeting new people, and I do have to say that I have gotten out of touch with nature but that’s because I haven’t found someone to go exploring in the outdoors with. Camping, hiking, exploring etc., are all things that I miss in my life. I would say that I am always up for new adventures with friends and family.
